[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "装甲车最终抵达了荒漠的边界。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这里并没有什么特别的地方，放眼望去，前方依然是看不到尽头的黄沙。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但我和恩雅都沉默下来。我们都很清楚，这里的确就是这个世界的终点了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我加足了马力，装甲车无声地驰骋在荒漠之上，眼看离边界就只有一分钟不到的车程。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我随即侧过身子，轻轻捂住了恩雅的眼睛，自己也闭上了双眼。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_01",
        "zh_CN": "亲爱的？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "对于我的动作，恩雅显然有些惊讶。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "别怕，很快就好。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_02",
        "zh_CN": "我不是害怕，我只是在想……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她抓住了我的手，言语中带着难以言喻的平静。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_03",
        "zh_CN": "你在做不确定的事情时，总是会闭上眼睛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_04",
        "zh_CN": "但我想，不需要抗拒这里的一切，我们应该也可以出去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "什……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "来不及追问，车子便穿过了边界，周围的一切顿时被光芒笼罩。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "再睁开眼时，我们早已不在装甲车内。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "残破的建筑，空无一人的街道，损毁的汽车……熟悉的一切再次毫无保留地出现在我们眼前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "<span color=\"#ee4735\">显然，我们回到了16区。</>",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我第一时间朝着恩雅看去，如今我们回到了现实，那她的记忆也应该恢复了才对。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_05",
        "zh_CN": "我刚才……那是……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不出所料，恩雅难以置信地看向周围，又伸出手看了看自己，她脸上的表情与我在木屋里“回忆”起不存在的记忆时的表情几乎一模一样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-1",
        "Flag": "b-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "b-1-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "抱住她",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好了，都结束了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我紧紧抱住恩雅，一下一下地拍着她的后背，感受着她的颤抖慢慢平息。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们刚才只是做了一个很长的梦，一切都是16区的模因所导致的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "或许，还有一部分原因是恩雅当时想要保护我的愿望所产生的剧烈的情绪波动，但我并没有将这个猜测说出口。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_06",
        "zh_CN": "我们……从来没有一起去过什么荒漠，也没有自己建起木屋，是吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_07",
        "zh_CN": "那些，只不过是我自己的幻想……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但恩雅，你的幻想的确把我从危险中拯救了出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我低下头，捧住了恩雅的脸。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果没有恩雅在的话，我脑中那些混乱的模因很可能已经摧毁了我的意识。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_08",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "恩雅沉默着，握紧了自己的拳头。正当我担心起她的状态时，她忽然抬起手，用力揉了揉自己的脸。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "总是以姐姐自居的恩雅很少做出如此可爱的动作，我不由得露出了微笑。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_09",
        "zh_CN": "我还要保护分析员，必须要打起精神来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她一边说着，一边环顾起四周。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_10",
        "zh_CN": "我能感觉到这里的泰坦物质浓度很高，所以我们应该比之前更靠近16区的中心。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "说完，她又凑到我的身前，在我身上摸索起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你要找什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_11",
        "zh_CN": "通讯终端……我的应该是弄丢了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我从口袋中拿出终端递给了她，她快速戳了两下，又很快摇了摇头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_12",
        "zh_CN": "不行，这里果然还是没办法发出通讯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_13",
        "zh_CN": "当务之急，是尽快撤离到城市外围，在通讯不会受到干扰的地方与茉莉安取得联系。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_14",
        "zh_CN": "现在……没有时间留给我自责。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在说这些话时，她的眼中还带着未干的泪花，但这丝毫没有影响恩雅眼中的决意。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "的确，现在纠结不定，反倒是我太小看恩雅了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我一直都知道，恩雅·墨尔菲，从来不是一个会因为挫折就放弃前进的人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但我也清楚，这并不代表她不需要被照顾，只不过是因为她习惯了把伤疤藏在别人——甚至连自己都不容易看到的地方。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "望着她伸来的手，我毫不犹豫地搭了上去，并用更加坚决的力度将她拉入怀中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们出发吧，恩雅。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_15",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，出发吧，分析员！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "话虽如此，要找到前往城市外围的路却并不容易。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这座城市的中心被破坏得很严重，在钢筋水泥所组成的森林中，我们几乎无法辨认出方向。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "现在只能走一步看一步，抱着这样的心情，我和恩雅挑选了一条相对宽敞的道路向前走去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_16",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，我在想一件事情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "关于16区的模因吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_17",
        "zh_CN": "是的，分析员应该也很在意吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_18",
        "zh_CN": "我们从进入这里之后，一直被这所谓的模因牵着鼻子走，但归根结底，我们对模因还一无所知。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "的确，我们对模因的认知几乎都是来自于莉琪，而她那样子，总给人一种不靠谱的感觉。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "说到她，也不知道她现在跑到哪去了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_19",
        "zh_CN": "莉琪很熟悉16区，我们和她分开时附近也没有敌人了，她应该不会有事。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_20",
        "zh_CN": "我是在担心，如果在我们前进时又出现了其他模因的影响，让我们和那支军方小队一样迷失方向，那就糟糕了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_21",
        "zh_CN": "所以我想要了解更多关于模因的事情，如果能找到抵抗模因，甚至是能够反过来利用模因帮助我们的办法，就更好了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "利用模因……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看来恩雅的想法比我预想的还要更激进一些。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_22",
        "zh_CN": "不过，现在应该也没有调查模因的机会了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不……硬要说的话，实际上是有的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_dlc15ep3_girl011_23",
        "zh_CN": "哎？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我停下步子，指了指自己的脑袋。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那个光团中的被我吸收的模因，还有一部分残留在我的意识中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "恩雅澜风",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
